author: Kwanwoo Jun
title: South Korea GDP Grows 1.2% in Third Quarter
text:
SEOUL—South Korea’s economy picked up speed to a five-year high in the third quarter, aided by a stimulus-driven rebound in demand that outweighed the negative effect on exports of slowing Chinese and global demand.
